  "detailed_description": "《仙路志异》是一款Roguelike的战棋策略游戏。操作不同的角色，在随机地图中做出选择，构建独特的技能体系，获取最终胜利。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >并非正经的修仙故事</h2>绝天地通的千年后，曾经的仙神试图重返人间。<br>于是仙路悄无声息的出现在这个世界，选中之人被吞入其中，遵从仪轨，互相厮杀……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作天赋各异的角色</h2>每个角色都有其独特的主动技能和被动技能，这些将成为战斗胜利的关键。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566720/extras/114229f4dcd91d5c6ef0deaa9fe94e27.poster.avif?t=1657197628\" width=590 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566720/extras/114229f4dcd91d5c6ef0deaa9fe94e27.webm?t=1657197628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566720/extras/114229f4dcd91d5c6ef0deaa9fe94e27.mp4?t=1657197628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构建强大的队伍</h2>在地图中获得不同的技能、咒物来强化角色和队伍，组合出强大的战斗Build。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566720/extras/c66faf383fcf55e905fc895ba181d4c2.poster.avif?t=1657197628\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566720/extras/c66faf383fcf55e905fc895ba181d4c2.webm?t=1657197628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566720/extras/c66faf383fcf55e905fc895ba181d4c2.mp4?t=1657197628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>仙路志异交流群：945665108",
